 />\n咁我地唔鹹唔淡，見到不公義係眼前發生既時候，企係度握緊拳頭握到岀血，但唔踏岀去既理由，係乜野？</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"閱讀理解滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文章主旨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351ae68ebf3fe016afe2c51442504c88bf02289f","tid":1574118,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"85ca9072a1e1c77e7df6970102df37b5b8838692","tid":1574118,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:39:10.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"a155b3ede5b325a9592a70dd7b6ac7e212dad969","tid":1574118,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"73dd51817f0fe5370582e1166b321f47534e8326","tid":1574118,"uid":274725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669623337b4e3f58cddbdd5910514591c5f6df7f","tid":1574118,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1102f312aac2d548198e2009f3ee55b536efad5b","tid":1574118,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"2329318b9d1377c0ebcfe8fdc5a8f90980fea54d","tid":1574118,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:41:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">見到不公義係眼前發生既時候，企係度握緊拳頭握到岀血，但唔踏岀去既理由，係乜野？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3ff6f5cbc4da72b1286db0f871f38b879b2ecc7a","tid":1574118,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:41:23.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"cd22a645587eac9627ef6a72d9e8f70215853279","tid":1574118,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:42:54